markets.title: Will President Biden and Trump debate on Jun 27, 2024?
markets.subtitle: Unemployment
markets.rules_primary: If President Biden or former President Trump says Unemployment (or a tense/pluralization/grammatical inflection thereof), then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The exact phrase/word, or variations in tense/pluralization/grammatical inflection (e.g. “tariff” or “tariffs”), must be used; similar topics are not encompassed by the Payout Criterion (e.g., “health care” would not fulfill the “Obamacare” strike). Kalshi employees will gather the data used to resolve the market by following the debates as they are aired on television. Three members of Kalshi's team will watch the debate prior to the Contract’s Expiration and will attempt to form a consensus on whether or not the Payout Criterion has been fulfilled. If they do not form a consensus, the market does not resolve to Yes.
